title: Employee Management System
description: This EMS application hosted through React + Vite is a game-changing solution that redefines workforce administration. With multi-level access control, effortlessly manage multiple admins and employee logins, while conducting CRUD operations on a dynamic employee database.

title: Type Racer
description: A dynamic platform that allows assessment of user typing skills including typing speed (WPM) and incorrect character count. Sentences can be customized. The typing test history and statistics are updated and viewable in Game History to track typing progress!

title: Business Sentiment Analyzer
description: This Business Sentiment Analyzer application hosted through a robust Django web framework helps inform the way businesses interpret customer feedback. This application seamlessly integrates natural langugae processing techniques using PyTorch, Hugging Face Transformers, and a pre-trained BERT model for accurate sentiment analysis.

title: Review-Rating Linear Regression
description: Ths project is centered around the factors that contribute to the rating of a recipe. Specifically, the relationship between the average rating a recipe has, accumulated from all of it's individual user ratings, and the preparation time of the recipe. Are recipes rated independently from it's preparation time?

title: Predictive Modeling of Cardiovascular Disease
description: In our study, we deployed an XGBoost machine learning model to investigate the predictors of cardiovascular disease (CVD) outcomes within a dataset comprising 70,000 individual records. Our analysis focused on a comprehensive range of factors including cholesterol levels, blood pressure (both systolic and diastolic), glucose levels, smoking status, alcohol consumption, and physical activity.
